snippet.title: Match Highlights - Brazil 4:1 South Korea - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Brazil stormed into the quarterfinals of the #FIFAWorldCup for a record 17th time after beating South Korea 4-1 at Stadium 974.

The five-time champions stormed to a four-goal lead in the first half through goals from Vinicius Jr, Neymar, Richarlison & Lucas Paqueta.

Tite's side took the foot off the gas in the second half to see out the match. Paik Seung-ho pulled one back for the Asian side with a long-range effort and that was to be the only goal in the final 45 minutes.

Brazil will now face Croatia in the quarter-final on Dec 9, 8:30 pm.

Enjoy the highlights of #BRAKOR & stay tuned to #JioCinema & #Sports18 for more from the #WorldsGreatestShow 📺📲

Lyrics: 
Unna paathu sirichaa 
Adha ullukkulla nerupaakku 
Avamaanam kedachaa 
adhil greedam onna uruvaakku 
Unna kuththi ulagame 
aanandham adayume 
Thiruppi adikkum bodhu dhaan yaaru neennu puriyume 
Its time its time to give it:u back:u maame 
Idhu thiruppi idhu thiruppi kudukkum neram maame 
Udanja megame maa mazhaya kudukkume 
Kizhinja vedhayile thaan kaadu porakkume 
Pudhiya edhiriye vaa ennai edhirkave 
Pazhaya edhirigal en rasigar padayile 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Pera kettaa whistle adi 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Unga nenjin adhipathi 
Stanza 
Kaayam poruthu Sendru pazhagu mul irukkum vazhiyile 
Kooda nadandha kootta satham pullarikkum udalile 
Kaalgal thadukki malayil irundhu keezhe pogum nodiyile 
Kaigal asaithu paaru pudhiya rekkai pirakkum vazhiyile 
Kanneero 
Nee unakku sollum aaraaro 
Kan thoongi ezhundha pinbu nee vero 
Udanja megame maa mazhaya kudukkume 
Kizhinja vedhayile thaan kaadu porakkume 
Pudhiya edhiriye vaa ennai edhirkave 
Pazhaya edhirigal en rasigar padayile 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Pera kettaa whistle adi 
Thee idhu Thalapathee 
Unga nenjin adhipathi

snippet.title: Match Highlights - Argentina 2:1 Australia - FIFA World Cup Qatar 2022 | JioCinema & Sports18
snippet.description:
Argentina booked their place in the last eight for the 10th time in #FIFAWorldCup history, edging Australia 2-1 at the Ahmad bin Ali Stadium.

Lionel Messi, who hadn't scored in the knockout stages of the competition, opened the scoring in the 35th minute. Julian Alvarez doubled the lead for Lionel Scaloni's side after making the most of an error by Socceroos goalkeeper Mathew Ryan.

Australia pulled one back through an unfortunate own goal by Enzo Fernandez. But Argentina held their nerve to make it through.

Watch Messi & Co. next in action against #Netherlands in the quarter-final on Dec 9 - 8:30 pm, LIVE on #JioCinema & #Sports18 📺📲

snippet.title: FRENCH FRIES | Crispy French Fried potatoes Recipe Cooking In Village | Finger Chips | Easy Snacks
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook a French Fried Potato recipe. This French Fries recipe is a simple and easy snack recipe that everyone can cook quickly at home. We first boiled the sliced potatoes, then we sun dried them to make crispy Frech Fries.

Finally, we eat this snack in the evening by adding some hand-ground species masalas. Yummy and Crispy.

Dhyan Sreenivasan is an Indian actor, and film director who works in Malayalam films. Dhyan Sreenivasan made his acting debut with Thira, directed by Dhyan Sreenivasan elder brother Vineeth Sreenivasan. Dhyan is the younger son of noted actor and screenwriter Sreenivasan. Dhyan Sreenivasan brother Vineeth Sreenivasan is a singer, actor and director who also works in Malayalam cinema. Dhyan married his longtime girlfriend Arpita Sebastian on 7 April 2017. He made his film debut with the Malayalam film Thira which has Shobana in main lead role. In the film, Dhyan Sreenivasan did a supporting role along with two-time National Award winning actress Shobana. His performance in the film was generally well-received by critics and the audience.

snippet.title: Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM
snippet.description:
Filmymoji || Middle Class Madhu || Saradaaga || A Family Picnic || MCM

In this new saradaga episode of Middle Class Madhu, a funny discussion starts between 1A Master and his wife Bhagyam. The discussion later turns into a serious plan when Bhagyam asks him to plan a picnic with the colony. She motivates 1A Master to be the mastermind behind the picnic plan while they portray the plan being executed by Sarada Subbarao. Finally, after convincing sarada Subba Rao, the picnic plan gets started. In surprise, Budatha invites his girlfriend Geetha to the picnic. Seeing Geetha madhu surprises him and he tries to put a fight between Geetha and Budatha, but his plan turns out to be profitable for Budatha. Everybody enjoys the places in Vizag, and Madhu, with his Naatu Guntala Gang, starts funny plans to make the picnic even more funnier. 1A master who is so excited and looking happy in the picnic was the target for Madhu and His Gang. Watch out for this fun-filled episode, Saradaga! And we promise you a 30-minute fun ride.

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Siyani Episode 113 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 5th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Anmol Baloch - Kiran
Usama Khan - Zohaib
Saniya Shamshad - Ujala
Mohsin Abbas Haider - Zarbaab
Erum Akhter - Reema
Tipu Shareef - Bakhtiyar
Parveen Akbar - Fazeelat
Beena Chaudhary - Nusrat
Hashim Butt

snippet.description:
New Christmas Song 2022 | #drsatishkumar | New Song | Calvary Temple Songs| Latest Christmas Song Trending Christmas Song

Lyrics : Dr.Satish Kumar
Tune : Bro.Sunil
Music : Bro.Anup Rubens

రచన: Dr. సతీష్ కుమార్ 
సంగీతం : Bro.అనూప్ రూబెన్స్
స్వర కల్పన: Bro. సునీల్

మనిషిని ప్రాణంగా ప్రేమించిన దేవుడు,
మనిషికై ప్రాణాన్ని అర్పించిన నాథుడు -2 
మనకోసమే నేడు జన్మించెను చూడు -2 
హల్లేలూయ పాడు, సంతోషమే నేడు...

ప్రవచనాలన్నియు నెరవేర్చినె నాడు,
ప్రపంచాన్ని రక్షింప జన్మించే నేడు,
పశువుల పాకలో పవలించెనే-2 
పరలోకమే ప్రస్తుతించేనే -2 

పాపులందరిని ప్రేమించిన వాడు,
పాపుల రక్షణకై ప్రాణం పెట్టినవాడు,
పశువుల పాకలో పవలించెనే-2 
పరలోకమే ప్రస్తుతించేనే -2 

మనకోసమే నేడు జన్మించెను చూడు -2 
హల్లేలూయ పాడు, సంతోషమే నేడు...      " - పాపిని ప్రాణంగా"

Dear Man Of God Dr Satish Kumar surrendered his entire life to serve mankind. His powerful yet simple life changing teachings have attracted countless millions of people and transformed their lives from wickedness to Godliness. He is highly accepted and respected by all the regions and religious people because he never complains, condemns, criticizes or compares other Gods or religions. His teachings are most convicting people of their wicked ways rather than converting people.
         
           Great man Of God Dr Satish Kumar being an Indian highly speaks of India on international platforms about Indian values, culture and family structure.  He emphasizes “Service to mankind is service to God "and as Jesus said  "Love your neighbor as you love yourself".He believes this – thus he practices. 

     Great Man Of God  Dr SatishKumar's sermons are powerful and life changing that leads a blessed and prosperous spiritual life. He preaches on life-related topics that hold great interest for everyone, topics like acceptance, brokenness, calling, comfort, crisis, decisions, doubt, endurance, giving, healing, hurts, loss, love, miracles, mistakes, planning, purpose, risk, stress, temptation, tragedy, and wisdom etc

snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Farq Episode 11 - [Eng Sub]- Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 5th December 2022 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3633 - 5 Dec 2022 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3633
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide's uncle pays a visit to him who is looking for a suitable spouse for Vidya. Popatlal is listening to their conversation and is pleased that Bhide has been given the task of finding Vidya a suitable spouse. However, Popatlal is surprised when Bhide tells his uncle that he is unaware of any such groom. Excited Popatlal confronts Bhide as the visitors leave his home and requests that he suggest his name for Vidya. Bhide informs him that since their uncle solely wants a teacher for Vidya, his decision is peculiar. Popatlal, who was ecstatic about the wedding, requests that he give him Vidya's contact information because he wants to speak with her and discuss her concerns. Bhide is aggravated by Popatlal's actions and asks him to leave. Watch the episode.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3633, 5 Dec 2022
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000198072

snippet.title: 🥰 Vaishali ku Naanga kodutha Surprise || Doctor Vaishali is Back 😍|| Oru Long Drive Polama Makkale
snippet.description:
Hey guys! Welcome to our channel! So what's the best way to celebrate comebacks? Sometime back, Vaishali returned home as a doctor. Living away from home for years and coming back called for a grand welcome.  

This vlog is unique as I welcome Vaishali home with a special gift, a Tata Tigor car, waiting to surprise her! It's a complete joy to see her home, and this moment gets more joyful with the brand-new Tata Tigor. There's no better way than gifting my lady luck a brand-new car and making her feel butterflies all over again!
  
Tata Tigor is India's Safest Sedan, a sub-compact, stylish, and when it hits the road, the world stops and stares! Join us to make this moment of our life worthwhile with love and blessings as we bring this special gift home!
Know more: https://cars.tatamotors.com/cars/tigor

#TataTigor #Tigor #TataMotors #arunaravind #vaishalipriya #nilannavilan #arunaravindtwins

snippet.description:

Returning to the action and spectacle that have captured moviegoers around the world, Transformers: Rise of the Beasts will take audiences on a ‘90s globetrotting adventure and introduce the Maximals, Predacons, and Terrorcons to the existing battle on earth between Autobots and Decepticons. Directed by Steven Caple Jr. and starring Anthony Ramos and Dominique Fishback, the film arrives in theatres June 9, 2023.

snippet.title: Siyani Mega Ep 112 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 4th Dec 2022
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Siyani Mega Ep 112 - [Eng Sub] - Anmol Baloch - Mohsin Abbas Haider -Saniya Shamshad - 4th December 2022

Hailing from a lower-middle-class family, Kiran is a selfish and arrogant girl who aspires to achieve a lifestyle through mending her ways and taking shortcuts. Kiran’s mother Nusrat Ara is aware of her daughter’s nature and doesn’t stop her from doing anything. On the contrary, Ujala is a well-mannered and beautiful girl who lives with Kiran’s family and strives to become independent. 

Zarbab, a handsome young man who belongs to an influential and wealthy family. His first meeting with Kiran turns out to be magical as he falls in love at first sight. Kiran sees him as a way to advance forward in life and builds a web of lies and deceit around Zarbab. On the other hand, Ujala is forced to live a life deprived of love and unfulfilled dreams.

Will Ujala ever find the love and respect that she deserves? After building her life on lies and deception, how long will Kiran be able to conceal the truth?

Written By: Sadia Akhtar
Directed By: Ali Akbar
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Anmol Baloch - Kiran
Usama Khan - Zohaib
Saniya Shamshad - Ujala
Mohsin Abbas Haider - Zarbaab
Erum Akhter - Reema
Tipu Shareef - Bakhtiyar
Parveen Akbar - Fazeelat
Beena Chaudhary - Nusrat
Hashim Butt

Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats.

snippet.description:
HEY GUYS !!!
This Video has everything that happens in Indian Schools . The most relatable and Netflix Binge Watching Video  . Scenarios like what happens on Indian Mom who loves her Tv Serials like anupama and Old Bollywood Movies being big fan of Amitabh Bachchan has now become Netflix lover and it excited for new season of stranger things , cleaning her whole house in advance so that she can sit all day long for being watching netflix show . Mummy loves eleven , Steve Harrington , Maa vs beti , daughter loves eddie Munson . k drama lovers Going to asian restaurants eating sushi , struggle of eating with chopsticks , dimsums , dreaming about seoul korean food , bts , bts army , persuading best friend to watch k Drama , Talking about Korean boys , using words like sarange , Finger heart , naming best Korean shows like what's wrong with secretary , Mom dad enjoying old bollywood movie and daughter pissed off with bollywood cliche villain girl being hot and career oriented and has short hair , rich dad buying beti ka bf with his daulat , sisters doing movie marathon on hotstar , amazon prime , netflix new horror suspense series wednesday , sister using her phone while watching , taking multiple pee breaks , struggle of watching movie in Movie theatre you can rewind or pause like home , or can't skip boring stuff , dreaming about boys in netflix shows , and real life Boyfriend has full beard because of No shave November . Night Stay at Friend house , her Mom feeding ou Favourite Idli Sambhar , Rajma Chawal , Aunty loves her cooking skills and praises for that . Netflix and Chill , Genz addicted to watching series , shows , movies on Netflix like  Friends , The Vampire diaries , Superstore Money Heist, , Lucifer , Schitt's Creek , Those Netflix freaks who eats while watching shows , Before sleeping also binge watches content on OTT , Or Laughing Hard On Hindi Dubbed Hollywood Movies , Like fast and Furious , Avengers age of ultron in hindi dubbing is too funny , indian Middle class family watching Bridgerton in Hindi and Missing the Sexy British accent , Whole family getting awkward because of the adult scenes in bridgeton beti pissed off with Mom for sharing her netflix password with every person in whole india .  
 .. Relive and Relish your Tv bingewatching life.. These are the best days of getting convered into a BingeWatcher .

snippet.title: Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Ep. 552 | Kabir's Secret Is Exposed | खुल गया कबीर का राज़
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

While Sankar is happy with Kabir's victory, Thapki is heartbroken by the Pandey family losing their home. But fate has some other plans as Thapki comes across Neha and recognizes her. She takes her to Pandey house and exposes Kabir's lie. Soon Thapki is stunned by another shocking revelation about Bihaan. 

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

Watch more videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLX18mvVSh-bzmIBfH3sKcKbGZQJ_OGGIg

snippet.title: Shakti | शक्ति | Ep. 669 | Soumya Rejects The Truth | सौम्या ने ठुकराया सच
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Harman takes Soumya on a date and at the venue, shows her some of her photographs taken before her memory loss hoping to trigger her memory. But this plan backfires when she refuses to believe him and burns the photographs, warning him against pursuing her ever again. How will Harman handle this failure?

Set against the backdrop of culturally rich and vibrant Punjab, Shakti-Astitva Ke Ehsaas Ki portrays the power of a family to dictate the fate of its daughters, Soumya and Surbhi. Deprived of an education, companions and toys, Soumya can't understand the indifference her father and Dadi show towards her and finds solace only in her mother's arms. Meanwhile Surbhi gets everything she wants, except for the one thing she yearns for-her mother's love. What has caused these heart-breaking rifts in this otherwise perfect family? What makes parents discriminate between their own daughters? Watch the mystery unfold.

Watch more videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLX18mvVSh-bxRAKAf77tUWcNIEnPEeB-b

snippet.title: Thapki Pyar Ki | Ep. 551 | Thapki Conquers Pandey Niwas | थपकी ने पांडे निवास पर की विजय प्राप्त
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

As the match advances towards the end, the battle to conquer Pandey Niwas intensifies. Despite dislocating his shoulder, Bihaan puts up a heroic show, but fails to steer his team towards victory. Thapki and her team win the cricket match and Thapki conquers Pandey Niwas. 

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

Watch more videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLX18mvVSh-bzmIBfH3sKcKbGZQJ_OGGIg

snippet.title: Resham Ka Rumal | Divya Agarwal | Shruti Rane | Official Music Video | Latest Hindi Song 2022
snippet.description:
"Resham Ka Rumal" has always been a song to sway your legs. Bringing a modern and uplifting rendition with lyrics penned by Rajesh Manthan and a modern mood by Gourov Dasgupta. Sung by Shruti Rane and featuring none other than Divya Agarwal. The video is directed and choreographed by Prince Gupta.

Buy Carvaan Mobile- Feature phone with 1500 Pre-loaded songs at http://sarega.ma/ycmbuy

Credits:
Featuring: Divya Agarwal
Director & Choreographer – Prince Gupta
Singer- Shruti Rane
D.O.P. – Ajay Pandey
Stylist- Jimmy Z
Music – Gourov Dasgupta  
Programmed, mixed and mastered – Som Riggs
Lyricist- Rajesh Manthan                                                                  
Editor -Oswin Reveredo (Shake & Cut Studio)
Asst. editor - Ulleses Correia 
Production house – Prince Gupta Films
Executive Producer - Prayas Choudhary
Assistant Choreographers - Ali Choudary, Rupali Kantharia, Bhavika Sachdeva, Shubham 
Director’s associate- Paraag Choudhary
Art - Amrita Maruti Pawadmal
Divya’s Team:
Manager- Esha 
Make Up- Disha Girish Sanghvi
Assistant - Nirmal Shah and Akshay
Hairstyle- Mohammed Irfan Shaikh
Prince Gupta Film Team: Kamal Singh Bathi , Durgesh Sambariya, Vishal Vedre, Saiprasad Amare , Sujit 

Original Credits:
Original Music Director: Ila Arun, Lalit Sen
Original Singer: Ila Arun
Original Lyrics: Ila Arun

Lyrics:
Dum dum damke jhumka mera, maarda lashkaara,

Rang birangi odhni main, odh aayi yaara,

Sun zara bole kya dil ka iktara..

Resham ka.. haan
Resham ka roomal gale mein daal ke,  tu aaja na.. aa wait karoon main, 

Main cherry wali lipistick lagake, arey.. kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..

Resham ka.... haan

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham bole, Re ,

Meri nathani haale dole, mera bichhua chham chham bole..

Meri laal chunariya, sar se sarakati jaaye

Dildaar mere main, haan branded wala perfume lagaake are, kab se chhupi hoon mai rajaayi mein, o o

Resham ka.. Haan

Jab jab dekhoon chehra tera,
Hosh huye aawaara
Bajaran teri huyi main,
Tu mera banjaara,

Dholna  sabse tu mujhko hai pyaara,

Resham ka...
Resham ka roomal gale mein daalke tu aa jaana, darling mere main,. Main mehngi waali goggle lagake yaham  kab se khadi hoon darwajje pe..oo

Resham ka...

Mai cherry wali lipistick lagake are
Mai mehengi wali goggle lagake aha
Han branded wala perfume lagake  

Kabse khadi hun darawajje pe,o o o
Resham Ka.. Haa
